Package ru.ewc.decita

Class Locators

java.lang.Object
ru.ewc.decita.Locators
public final class Locators extends Object
I am the collection of Locators used to populate the ComputationContexts. My main responsibility is to keep track of the Locators, merge them together and provide the merged result.
Since:
0.3.1
